duck: Carroll Izard - Carroll Ellis Izard is an American psychologist known for his contributions to Differential Emotions Theory, and the Maximally Discriminative Affect Coding System.
Interesting (The Young Ones) - "Interesting" was the fifth episode of British sitcom The Young Ones.
Ecstasy (emotion) - Ecstasy is a subjective experience of total involvement of the subject, with an object of his or her awareness.
Surprise - Surprise is a brief emotional state experienced as the result of an unexpected event.
Interest is a feeling or emotion that causes attention to focus on an object, event, or process.
Curiosity - Curiosity is a quality related to inquisitive thinking such as exploration, investigation, and learning, evident by observation in human and many animal species.
